## Packaging a build

When tests pass and the work is ready for acceptance:

```bash
/scripts/package.sh          # pushes ${REGISTRY}:dev-<sha> and ${REGISTRY}:dev
/scripts/package.sh rc1      # also tags as :rc1
```

Then open a PR so the user can review and promote.

---

## Constraints

- Do not push to the upstream repo directly вЂ” PRs to your fork only
- Do not merge your own PRs
- Do not attempt to reach or modify acceptance or production
- Do not commit secrets or tokens
